       </em>
       mice were analyzed using FACS for binding to fibronectin (FN7-10 fragment) or 9EG7 antibody (n=6 mice/genotype). Shown are the mean fluorescence intensities relative to WT splenocytes, and representative histograms. (
       <strong>
        c
       </strong>
