        cpdm
       </em>
       MEFs (left). Binding of fibronectin (FN7-10 fragment) to WT and
       <em>
        cpdm
       </em>
       MEFs (right) was analyzed using FACS (n=4). Binding to WT cells is assigned value 1.0. (
