       mice were transfected with full-length α5-GFP WT or α5-GFP 34AA mutant and the α5β1-integrin activity was analysed with SNAKA51 antibody using FACS. Shown are mean fluorescence intensities of SNAKA51 stainings relative to GFP intensity (the intensity of WT MEFs expressing WTα5 is defined as 1.0) (n=3). (
       <strong>
