       </strong>
       ) Binding of fibronectin (FN7-10 fragment) to
       <em>
        cpdm
       </em>
       MEFs transfected with GFP or GFP-SHARPIN in the presence or absence of membrane-permeable SHARPIN binding α-tail peptide (α1-TAT) or scramble peptide (ScrTAT) was analyzed using FACS (n=3). Ctrl, control without peptides.
